  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.58,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.58,
      "end": 3.8,
      "text": "9월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.8,
      "end": 6.46,
      "text": "농아인 가족과 세상을 연결하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.46,
      "end": 8.18,
      "text": "한 소녀의 이야기를 그린"
    },
    {
      "start": 8.18,
      "end": 9.14,
      "text": "코우라"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.14,
      "end": 10.5,
      "text": "와 어서 오세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 10.5,
      "end": 12.42,
      "text": "Hey there it's good to be back"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.42,
      "end": 14.0,
      "text": "예 굿모닝입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.0,
      "end": 14.96,
      "text": "굿모닝 여러분"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.96,
      "end": 16.1,
      "text": "굿모닝 로라님"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.1,
      "end": 20.68,
      "text": "네 2021년 올해 썬댄스 영화제에서요"
    },
    {
      "start": 20.68,
      "end": 23.26,
      "text": "4관왕을 차지한 영화래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.26,
      "end": 25.26,
      "text": "심사위원 대상도 받고"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.26,
      "end": 28.72,
      "text": "감독상에 관객상에 앙상블상에"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.72,
      "end": 32.74,
      "text": "아주 올해 최고 음악 영화로 평가를 받은 작품이라고 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.74,
      "end": 35.46,
      "text": "Yeah the music was really something in this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.46,
      "end": 35.82,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.82,
      "end": 36.66,
      "text": "Powerful"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.66,
      "end": 37.12,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.12,
      "end": 39.68,
      "text": "And it was not only the music"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.68,
      "end": 41.48,
      "text": "But it was the contrast"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.48,
      "end": 44.44,
      "text": "Between the music and the silence"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.44,
      "end": 46.82,
      "text": "Because the actors are deaf"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.82,
      "end": 47.28,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.28,
      "end": 48.38,
      "text": "The main actors"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.38,
      "end": 49.44,
      "text": "Except the girl"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.44,
      "end": 52.5,
      "text": "So we get to hear from their perspective"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.5,
      "end": 53.0,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.0,
      "end": 54.2,
      "text": "They can't hear the music"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.2,
      "end": 54.76,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.76,
      "end": 57.7,
      "text": "So it gave me an indirect experience"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.7,
      "end": 58.32,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.32,
      "end": 60.12,
      "text": "진짜 그 장면 너무 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.12,
      "end": 62.34,
      "text": "심금을 울렸다고 해야 되나"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.34,
      "end": 64.7,
      "text": "약간 숙연해지기도 하고 그랬어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.7,
      "end": 66.28,
      "text": "The contrast between the music"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.28,
      "end": 67.54,
      "text": "And then the silence"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.54,
      "end": 67.86,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.86,
      "end": 68.86,
      "text": "It goes back and forth"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.86,
      "end": 69.12,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.12,
      "end": 71.84,
      "text": "So actually the director of the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.84,
      "end": 72.88,
      "text": "Sean Hayder"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.88,
      "end": 74.58,
      "text": "She said in an interview"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.58,
      "end": 76.3,
      "text": "That she knew the music"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.3,
      "end": 77.2,
      "text": "Was going to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.2,
      "end": 79.32,
      "text": "A very important part of the story"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.32,
      "end": 80.8,
      "text": "And how it would play"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.8,
      "end": 81.94,
      "text": "Against the silence"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.94,
      "end": 85.58,
      "text": "And one of her objectives"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.58,
      "end": 86.58,
      "text": "Or one of her goals"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.58,
      "end": 87.18,
      "text": "In this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.18,
      "end": 89.8,
      "text": "Was to go between the music"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.8,
      "end": 90.52,
      "text": "And the silence"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.52,
      "end": 93.12,
      "text": "And also to get the audience"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.12,
      "end": 94.4,
      "text": "To be more comfortable"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.4,
      "end": 95.52,
      "text": "With silence"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.52,
      "end": 96.02,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.02,
      "end": 96.98,
      "text": "Because often times"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.98,
      "end": 98.22,
      "text": "Especially on radio"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.22,
      "end": 98.6,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.6,
      "end": 100.12,
      "text": "We're not comfortable with silence"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.12,
      "end": 100.56,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.56,
      "end": 101.96,
      "text": "We need to feel the audio"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.96,
      "end": 102.4,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.4,
      "end": 103.62,
      "text": "빈 곳이 있으면 안 돼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.62,
      "end": 105.56,
      "text": "빈 부분이 있으면 식은 땀 나요"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.56,
      "end": 106.14,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.14,
      "end": 107.38,
      "text": "But in this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.38,
      "end": 107.92,
      "text": "It's different"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.92,
      "end": 108.34,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.34,
      "end": 109.48,
      "text": "We have picture"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.48,
      "end": 110.6,
      "text": "We have faces"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.6,
      "end": 113.24,
      "text": "And we can listen to the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.24,
      "end": 114.44,
      "text": "From her parents"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.44,
      "end": 115.7,
      "text": "Ruby's parents' perspective"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.7,
      "end": 117.64,
      "text": "And also her perspective"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.64,
      "end": 118.08,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.08,
      "end": 119.12,
      "text": "The deaf perspective"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.12,
      "end": 121.64,
      "text": "And also the normal hearing perspective"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.64,
      "end": 122.02,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.02,
      "end": 123.96,
      "text": "절묘한 감정"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.96,
      "end": 125.86,
      "text": "절묘한 순간순간"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.86,
      "end": 126.88,
      "text": "이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.88,
      "end": 129.46,
      "text": "특히 이 음악 공연을 하는 장면에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.46,
      "end": 131.14,
      "text": "루비의 부모님하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.14,
      "end": 133.36,
      "text": "루비의 오빠가 느끼는"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.36,
      "end": 134.04,
      "text": "그 silence"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.04,
      "end": 136.62,
      "text": "많이들 공감하셨을 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.62,
      "end": 136.88,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.88,
      "end": 137.4,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.4,
      "end": 138.94,
      "text": "오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.94,
      "end": 141.06,
      "text": "You're gonna avoid me until we graduate"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.06,
      "end": 143.68,
      "text": "I wasn't laughing at them for being death"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.68,
      "end": 144.56,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.56,
      "end": 146.06,
      "text": "It was the situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.06,
      "end": 146.94,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.94,
      "end": 148.8,
      "text": "Look I know it's not an excuse"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.8,
      "end": 150.52,
      "text": "But it sucks in my house right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.52,
      "end": 151.2,
      "text": "And you've got this like"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.2,
      "end": 151.96,
      "text": "Perfect life"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.96,
      "end": 152.26,
      "text": "And"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.26,
      "end": 152.74,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.3,
      "end": 154.36,
      "text": "Your parents are madly in love"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.36,
      "end": 155.86,
      "text": "They can't keep their hands off each other"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.86,
      "end": 156.54,
      "text": "And your house is"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.54,
      "end": 157.14,
      "text": "Disgusting"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.14,
      "end": 158.7,
      "text": "My house is disgusting"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.7,
      "end": 160.84,
      "text": "아 이 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.84,
      "end": 161.74,
      "text": "기억나세요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.04,
      "end": 163.28,
      "text": "Oh they had a fight"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.28,
      "end": 163.9,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.9,
      "end": 165.28,
      "text": "A pretty big fight"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.28,
      "end": 166.64,
      "text": "특히 저는"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.64,
      "end": 168.7,
      "text": "Miles가 disappointed me"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.7,
      "end": 169.24,
      "text": "Did he?"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.36,
      "end": 170.02,
      "text": "So much"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.02,
      "end": 171.28,
      "text": "You just don't like Miles"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.28,
      "end": 172.74,
      "text": "Why don't you like Miles?"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.8,
      "end": 173.82,
      "text": "What do you have against Miles?"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.94,
      "end": 174.18,
      "text": "아니"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.18,
      "end": 175.82,
      "text": "의도를 가지고 싫어하는 건 아니고"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.82,
      "end": 177.76,
      "text": "He should have not told it"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.76,
      "end": 178.86,
      "text": "To his friend"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.86,
      "end": 179.36,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.36,
      "end": 180.28,
      "text": "Even one person"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.28,
      "end": 180.9,
      "text": "That's true"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.9,
      "end": 182.52,
      "text": "He only told one guy"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.52,
      "end": 183.88,
      "text": "But you know high school"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.88,
      "end": 185.04,
      "text": "Rumors"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.04,
      "end": 186.12,
      "text": "Spreads fast"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.12,
      "end": 187.64,
      "text": "그리고 이런 명언도 있잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.64,
      "end": 189.48,
      "text": "그 saying 중에 뭐가 있냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.48,
      "end": 190.28,
      "text": "Bad news"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.28,
      "end": 191.98,
      "text": "Travels fast"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.98,
      "end": 192.64,
      "text": "Is that right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.76,
      "end": 194.0,
      "text": "Faster than good news"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.0,
      "end": 195.02,
      "text": "Of course"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.02,
      "end": 195.66,
      "text": "Rumors"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.66,
      "end": 196.82,
      "text": "People love gossip"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.82,
      "end": 199.66,
      "text": "And this was a funny story"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.66,
      "end": 200.14,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.14,
      "end": 201.36,
      "text": "So Ruby's parents"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.36,
      "end": 202.4,
      "text": "Embarrassed her"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.4,
      "end": 203.68,
      "text": "In front of Miles"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.68,
      "end": 204.68,
      "text": "And Miles"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.68,
      "end": 205.8,
      "text": "Thought it was funny"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.8,
      "end": 207.96,
      "text": "So he told one of his best friends"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.96,
      "end": 209.18,
      "text": "The story"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.18,
      "end": 210.3,
      "text": "And then"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.3,
      "end": 211.32,
      "text": "The news spread"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.32,
      "end": 212.22,
      "text": "Around the whole school"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.22,
      "end": 214.5,
      "text": "전교생이 다 알아버린"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.5,
      "end": 215.72,
      "text": "그런 사건이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.72,
      "end": 216.94,
      "text": "And everybody was laughing"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.94,
      "end": 219.04,
      "text": "When Ruby came to school"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.04,
      "end": 221.0,
      "text": "So she is furious"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.0,
      "end": 221.58,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.58,
      "end": 222.66,
      "text": "Really angry at Miles"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.66,
      "end": 223.02,
      "text": "Miles가"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.02,
      "end": 225.26,
      "text": "Ruby한테 사과를 했음에도 불구하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.26,
      "end": 225.88,
      "text": "She didn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.88,
      "end": 226.36,
      "text": "You know"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.36,
      "end": 227.5,
      "text": "Accept his apology"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.5,
      "end": 229.12,
      "text": "And he apologized"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.12,
      "end": 230.36,
      "text": "Very genuinely"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.36,
      "end": 230.92,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.92,
      "end": 231.92,
      "text": "I'm so sorry"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.92,
      "end": 234.26,
      "text": "저라도 아마"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.26,
      "end": 236.94,
      "text": "쉽게 용서를 못했을 것 같기는 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.94,
      "end": 237.34,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.46,
      "end": 237.7,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.7,
      "end": 238.6,
      "text": "It was definitely"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.6,
      "end": 240.5,
      "text": "Not a pretty situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.5,
      "end": 241.0,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.0,
      "end": 241.52,
      "text": "자"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.52,
      "end": 243.42,
      "text": "표현들 먼저 점검을 해볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.42,
      "end": 244.58,
      "text": "Avoid"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.58,
      "end": 245.58,
      "text": "Avoid"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.58,
      "end": 246.52,
      "text": "피하다"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.52,
      "end": 247.84,
      "text": "라는 동사입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.84,
      "end": 250.26,
      "text": "Madly in love"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.26,
      "end": 252.1,
      "text": "Madly in love"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.1,
      "end": 252.84,
      "text": "특히 그 앞에"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.84,
      "end": 255.08,
      "text": "비동사를 같이 붙여주시면"
    },
    {
